verse.lines:
{lang-eng}God is at work in us His purpose to perform,
Building a kingdom of power not of words,
Where things impossible by faith shall be made possible;
Let’s give the glory to Him now.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Though we are weak, His grace is everything we need;
We’re made of clay but this treasure is within.
He turns our weaknesses into His opportunities,
So that the glory goes to Him.{/lang-eng}
